OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'I knew who my burglar was 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F- police did nothing'      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A woman whose home was burgled as she  
OL,6, slept says the police would not        
OL,7, question the man she had identified    
OL,8, from CCTV as the offender.             
OL,10,FSarah Goode from Blackburn told BBC    
OL,11,FPanorama that officers "were not       
OL,12,Fprepared to do anything".              
OL,14,FThe programme investigated further and 
OL,15,Ffound more CCTV - it showed the        
OL,16,Foffender going in and out of her house.
OL,18,FLancashire Police says it recognises   
OL,19,Fthe impact crime has on victims and    
OL,20,Fthat tackling burglary is a priority.  
